# RUNTIME ML model artifacts written by PF-MLRetrain task. The
# `models/*.joblib` rule below only matches a top-level `models/` dir,
# so data/models/ needs its own entry. SNAPSHOT artifacts that should
# stay tracked (e.g. data/temporal_patterns.json) live in data/ root,
# not data/models/.
data/models/meta_learner_*.joblib
data/models/meta_learner_*_metrics.json

